  "problemSolved": {
    "statement": "Bytebase is an open-source database DevOps tool, it's the **only database CI/CD project** included by the [CNCF Landscape](https://landscape.cncf.io/?selected=bytebase&item=app-definition-and-development--continuous-integration-delivery--bytebase) and [Platform Engineering](https://platformengineering.org/tools/bytebase).",
